*Tip* se prenosi sa generacije na generaciju. (The tradition is passed down from generation to generation.)

Postoje mnogi *tipovi* obrazovanja. (There are many types of education.)

Dobro je poznavati različite *tipove* ljudi. (It's good to know different types of people.)

Ne postoji jedan univerzalni *tip* osobe. (There is no one universal type of person.)

Ona je vrlo odvažno prihvatila *tip* posla. (She bravely accepted the job.)